body:
Little Love: TFLN

*some smut

Evie - Harry

Can’t do any manual labour but Nora and I are sure working these overalls.

Don’t make me miss you anymore then I already do. Nora is growing so quickly. Tell her to slow down till I get back.

I wish she would slow down. She’s measuring small but she feels so big. I feel like a whale, need you to love me.

You don’t look like a whale baby. You look gorgeous and that bump suits you. 

Also if I have my way, after Nora’s first birthday you aren’t leaving the bedroom till I know you’re carrying my baby.

Remember how I told you I’m really horny all the time?

Very well baby, all I have is my memories of how wet you get.

Well at least you can reach down there so stop taunting me. Because until you get back I won’t be able to get off so just imagine how wet I will be for you.

Harry?

I see you read my text.

Harry???

Sorry, I had to do something. I miss you baby.

Harry, you shit. 

You started it by sending me that picture.

I’m sorry, I think I have a breeding kink.

I love you so much you know. Wish I was there with you know.

I love you to baby and all the other babies I am going to put in you.
